Package de.gmxhome.conrad.jpos.jpos_base.pointcardrw

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PointCardRWInterface
    Interface for methods that implement property setter and method calls for the PointCardRW device category.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Factory
    General part of PointCardRW factory for JPOS devices using this framework.
    PointCardRWDataEvent
    Data event implementation for PointCardRW devices.
    PointCardRWErrorEvent  
    PointCardRWOutputCompleteEvent  
    PointCardRWProperties
    Class containing the point card reader / writer specific properties, their default values and default implementations of PointCardRWInterface.
    PointCardRWService
    PointCardRW service implementation.
    PointCardRWService.EscAlignment
    Class describing alignment escape sequences ESC|xA, where x is one of c or r.
    PointCardRWService.EscEmbedded
    Class describing embedded escape sequences ESC|[*]#E.
    PointCardRWService.EscFontTypeface
    Class describing font typeface selection escape sequences ESC|#fT.
    PointCardRWService.EscNormalize
    Class describing normalize escape sequences ESC|N.
    PointCardRWService.EscScale
    Class describing scaling escape sequences ESC|[#][x]C, where x is one of h or v.
    PointCardRWService.EscSimple
    Class describing simple attribute setting escape sequences ESC|xC, where x is one of b, i or rv.
    PointCardRWService.EscUnderline
    Class describing line escape sequences ESC|[!][#]xC, where x is one of u or st.
    PointCardRWService.EscUnknown
    Class describing unknown escape sequence.
    PointCardRWService.PrintData
    Class describing printable part of print data.
    PointCardRWService.PrintDataPart
    Helper class used to control parsed output data.
    PointCardRWStatusUpdateEvent
    Status update event implementation for PointCardRW devices.
    PrintWrite
